Stock Market Dashboard:
A powerful and intuitive web application that provides stock market insights through interactive charts and data visualizations. 
The dashboard is designed to cater to users who wish to 
    analyze market trends, 
    view stock price variations, and 
    explore historical stock data.

Features:
    Real-time Stock Data: Fetches live stock market data for companies using yFinance.
    Interactive Charts: Displays stock trends, price variations, moving averages, and company statistics using Chart.js.
    Date Filters: Allows users to filter stock data by specific date ranges.
    Stock Search: Search for specific stock symbols to display tailored charts and metrics.
    Archived Data: View historical stock data in a tabular format for reference.
    Responsive Design: Fully responsive UI built using Bootstrap for seamless use across devices.
    User Authentication: Secure login and registration system with hashed passwords using Flask-Login.

Technologies Used:
Backend:
    Python
    Flask
    PostgreSQL
    SQLAlchemy
Frontend:
    HTML5
    CSS3
    Bootstrap
    Chart.js
    JavaScript
APIs:
yFinance (Yahoo Finance API) for fetching stock data.

